==آب او هوا==
Khash has a [[hot desert climate]] ([[Köppen climate classification|Köppen]] ''BWh''), characterised by little precipitation and high variation between summer and winter temperatures. The average temperature in Khash is 21.4 °C, while the annual precipitation averages 62 mm. July is the hottest month of the year with an average temperature of 34.4 °C. The coldest month January has an average temperature of 8.0 °C.

